extends layout

block content
  // Start Page Banner Area
  .page-banner-area
    .container-fluid
      .row.justify-content-center.align-items-center.g-4(data-cues='slideInUp' data-duration='1000')
        .col-xl-8.col-md-12
          .page-banner-content
            .content.section-title-animation.animation-style
              h2.title-animation Privacy Policy

  // Start Privacy Policy Content Area
  .ptb-120
    .container
      .row.justify-content-center
        .col-lg-10
          .policy-content
            p.last-updated 
              strong Last updated: 
              | 17/02/2026
            
            p Mamotechno Labs ("we", "our", "us") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.
            
            h3 1. Information We Collect
            p We may collect:
            ul
              li 
                strong Personal Information: 
                | name, email, phone number, company name (via contact forms)
              li 
                strong Technical Information: 
                | IP address, browser type, device information
              li 
                strong Usage Data: 
                | pages visited, time spent on the Website
            
            h3 2. How We Use Your Information
            p We use your information to:
            ul
              li Respond to inquiries
              li Provide services
              li Improve our Website and user experience
              li Communicate updates or business information
            
            h3 3. Cookies
            p We may use cookies or similar technologies to analyze traffic and improve functionality. You can disable cookies through your browser settings.
            
            h3 4. Data Sharing
            p We do not sell or rent your personal data.
            p We may share data only:
            ul
              li With service providers assisting us
              li If required by law
              li To protect our legal rights
            
            h3 5. Data Security
            p We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
            
            h3 6. Data Retention
            p We retain personal data only as long as necessary for business or legal purposes.
            
            h3 7. Your Rights
            p Depending on your location, you may have the right to:
            ul
              li Access your personal data
              li Request correction or deletion
              li Withdraw consent
            p To exercise these rights, contact us using the details below.
            
            h3 8. Third-Party Services
            p Our Website may use third-party tools (analytics, hosting, etc.). These services have their own privacy policies.
            
            h3 9. Children's Privacy
            p Our Website is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect children's personal data.
            
            h3 10. Changes to This Policy
            p We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Updates will be posted on this page.
            
            h3 11. Contact Us
            p For privacy-related questions, contact us at:
            p 
              i.fa-solid.fa-envelope
              |  
              a(href="mailto:info@mamotechnolabs.com") info@mamotechnolabs.com
  
  style.
    .policy-content {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 50px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .policy-content .last-updated {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .policy-content h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #111827;
      margin-top: 35px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .policy-content p {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .policy-content ul {
      margin-left: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .policy-content ul li {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .policy-content a {
      color: #1fa97f;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .policy-content a:hover {
      color: #0b3c3f;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .policy-content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .policy-content h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .policy-content p,
      .policy-content ul li {
        font-size: 15px;
      }
    }
